-- Nationwide Foreclosure Accord Deadline is Feb. 3, Nevada Says
-- B y   D a v i d   M c L a u g h l i n
-- 2012-01-30T18:55:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-30/proposed-nationwide-foreclosure-settlement-deadline-is-feb-3-nevada-says.html
State attorneys general have until
Feb. 3 to decide whether to sign on to a proposed nationwide
settlement of foreclosure wrongdoing with banks including  Bank
of America Corp. (BAC)  and  Citigroup Inc. (C)  that may total as much as
$25 billion, according to Nevada Attorney General Catherine
Cortez Masto.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David McLaughlin in New York at 
